            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"marimo-reactive-python-notebooks\">marimo \u2014 Reactive Python Notebooks</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>marimo</strong> reinvents the Python notebook:</span>\n<ul>\n<li>Cells re-run <strong>automatically</strong> when their dependencies change</li>\n<li>Stored as plain <code>.py</code> files \u2014 version-controllable &amp; importable</li>\n<li>Run as interactive apps <strong>or</strong> plain Python scripts</li>\n</ul></span>"
