            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h2 id=\"sidebar\">Sidebar</h2>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Open the <strong>left sidebar</strong> in the marimo editor:</span>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Packages</strong> tab \u2014 install packages on the fly</li>\n<li><strong>AI assistant</strong> tab \u2014 generate &amp; edit cells with an LLM</li>\n</ul>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><code>Cmd/Ctrl + Shift + P</code> opens the command palette.</span></span>"
